node.title: Armed police raid house in Christchurch, arrest one
node.description: Armed police were called to a Christchurch resident this morning.
node.content: ["Armed police were called to a Christchurch resident this morning.", "According to a statement from police, one person has been arrested at an address on Bealy Avenue and police are trying to locate a second person.", "Staff have been stood down.", "More to come"]
